{"tid":1155801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【皇室添丁】小熊維尼攀山涉水送禮 迪士尼窩心影片賀阿奇誕生","createTime":"2019-05-15T07:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T06:15:21.000Z","uid":130626,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"041660845dc8c2345d90a5e93fc0f98de85eec70","tid":1155801,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"英國薩塞克斯公爵夫人梅根順利在本月初誕下寶寶阿奇．哈里森．蒙巴頓－溫莎（Archie Harrison Mountbatten-Windsor），美國迪士尼公司也特地製作短片祝賀。<br />\n25秒的短片以水彩畫風為主，由資深的首席畫家雷文德（Kim Raymond）繪製。當中小熊維尼雙手捧着一本書皮為藍色、上面印有皇冠標誌的書，由牠和朋友一起居住的百畝森林（Hundred Acre Wood）出發。牠走過綠悠悠的草地，又跳過小河，長途跋涉將書本送抵溫莎堡（Windsor Castle），交到哈里和梅根手中。<br />\n片末為大廳之中，梅根坐在大椅上，和站在她身旁的哈里一同翻閱維尼的禮物，他們臉上都掛着笑容，而維尼也坐在他們旁邊觀望。畫面右方放置了一架嬰兒床，寫着「Archie」（阿奇）。<br />\n報道指，梅根當藝人之時，曾經在生活網站《The Tig》上寫網誌，並指由美國作者霍夫（Benjamin Hoff）所撰寫的《維尼之道》（The Tao Of Pooh，暫譯）是她最愛的書之一。2016年，英女皇也曾經「現身」於一本特別刊物中，當中維尼熊祝賀她90歲生日快樂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190514/large/1557829737_bc6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190514%2Flarge%2F1557829737_bc6d.jpg&h=0ab27522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190515/59598075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190515%2F59598075&d=UmPnmdD3xn3sHJtz75hgVwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=6d21b7c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190515%2F59598075&h=3cb01ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190515/59598075</a>"},{"pid":"34e856a78a41ae45f0c3c93cb20395b6ce5e521d","tid":1155801,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T22:28:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b59af2bf6bcd62fe53cab5678076117af7442aeb","tid":1155801,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T22:31:21.000Z","msg":"目測維尼身高170mm"},{"pid":"9fc933fd6c07584e4cccc9611a9cf4e4c6c4015a","tid":1155801,"uid":230428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T22:35:33.000Z","msg":"習近平俾人撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0485be0639d5acd2dcf48494aaea8f6812a1a302","tid":1155801,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc933fd6c07584e4cccc9611a9cf4e4c6c4015a","tid":1155801,"uid":230428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T22:35:33.000Z","msg":"習近平俾人撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T22:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該係我地太敏感"},{"pid":"62a53e59d57ff970962770392e9b9f3187095fcb","tid":1155801,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fc933fd6c07584e4cccc9611a9cf4e4c6c4015a","tid":1155801,"uid":230428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T22:35:33.000Z","msg":"習近平俾人撚狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}